<TITLE>
Gwelab'hot (Turn Over, Kelphit)
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Information and legends about the Native American mythological figure Gwelab'hot (Turn Over),
a medicine spirit child from the folklore of the Penobscot tribe.">
